      "name": "Crush",
      "type": "feat",
      "img": "icons/svg/aura.svg",
      "system": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>Rolagem de Ataque Corpo a Corpo: +5, alcance 1,5 m. Acerto: 6 (1d6 + 3) dano de concussão, and the darkmantle attaches to o alvo. If o alvo is a Medium or smaller creature and the darkmantle had Vantagem on a rolagem de ataque, it covers o alvo, which fica com a condição Cego and is suffocating while the darkmantle is attached in this way.\nWhile attached to a target, the darkmantle can attack only o alvo but has Vantagem on its attack rolls. Its Speed becomes 0, it can't benefit from any bonus to its Speed, and it moves with o alvo.\nA creature can take an action to try to detach the darkmantle from itself, doing so with a successful CD 13 Força (Athletics) check. On its turn, the darkmantle can detach itself by using 1,5 m of movement.</p>",
